    "row": 7,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 8,
    "rowsha": "/HCt7DrqPTKVOtr7v3jUHJV28EHoPj+WqrpaVZXkdS0=",
    "originContent": "It is blazing fast, built on the shoulders of giants:",
    "translatedContent": "它速度极快，建立在巨人的肩膀上："
  },
  {
