    "rowsha": "NLACtOPWs5fRM3uPvPibfOHj2tKtLvRH63fdRWe6PbM=",
    "originContent": "### As a standalone Mercure hub",
    "translatedContent": "### 作为独立的 Mercure hub 使用"
  },
  {
    "row": 21,
