  {
    "row": 27,
    "rowsha": "AM41j+0+MWwGeoCB2NEsUiyUZUZnetoY5q5V65SxZbo=",
    "originContent": "This will start a Freddie instance on `127.0.0.1:8080`, with anonymous subscriptions enabled.",
    "translatedContent": "这将在 `127.0.0.1:8080` 上启动一个 Freddie 实例，并启用匿名订阅。"
  },
  {
    "row": 28,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 29,
    "rowsha": "nroRAdraYLShNTbg5sNHvEsJvdIaeSqt7AajfTVCoLk=",
    "originContent": "You can publish updates to the hub by generating a valid JWT signed with the `!ChangeMe!` key with `HMAC SHA256` algorithm.",
    "translatedContent": "您可以通过生成一个使用 `!ChangeMe!` 密钥和 `HMAC SHA256` 算法签名的有效 JWT 来向集线器发布更新。"
  },
  {
    "row": 30,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 31,
    "rowsha": "6n8XgihmHEsjHUBwMzUKYn3hvywIVAs7aIFRG6xzLBk=",
    "originContent": "To change these values, see [Security](#security).",
    "translatedContent": "要更改这些值，请参见 [安全](#security)。"
  },
  {
    "row": 32,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 33,
    "rowsha": "WxLeKC7vq1A2gIR27p/XCXnVZt+FsvOPxOZ3LTl/8qQ=",
    "originContent": "### As a bundle of your existing Symfony application",
    "translatedContent": "### 作为您现有 Symfony 应用程序的一个捆绑包"
  },
  {
    "row": 34,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 35,
    "rowsha": "rTMjNc+qNIxb1xXDR5hEYiJw1fc4muBwuBsTXVIaIho=",
    "originContent": "```bash",
    "translatedContent": "```bash"
  },
  {
    "row": 36,
    "rowsha": "2P8yq2F59ONwoQ6HCYUdyyygqIOLR8H4ao46dzgR8hE=",
    "originContent": "composer req freddie/mercure-x",
    "translatedContent": "composer req freddie/mercure-x"
  },
  {
    "row": 37,
    "rowsha": "8bkBhHOQsO1+N058HkZOwXtGpCfEh6WtbL0pBkBQg9U=",
    "originContent": "```",
    "translatedContent": "```"
  },
  {
    "row": 38,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 39,
    "rowsha": "cWvUG3Y+/Cy8/jabJe86+qIkjyEHVJqTj1YM4pgNxtA=",
    "originContent": "You can then start the hub by doing:",
    "translatedContent": "然后您可以通过以下方式启动集线器："
  },
  {
    "row": 40,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 41,
    "rowsha": "rTMjNc+qNIxb1xXDR5hEYiJw1fc4muBwuBsTXVIaIho=",
    "originContent": "```bash",
    "translatedContent": "```bash"
  },
  {
    "row": 42,
    "rowsha": "LLe+cAXMkrBgbjvZwHAl2SNyyNztqiA+qwuK/9Otdjs=",
    "originContent": "bin/console freddie:serve",
    "translatedContent": "bin/console freddie:serve"
  },
  {
    "row": 43,
    "rowsha": "8bkBhHOQsO1+N058HkZOwXtGpCfEh6WtbL0pBkBQg9U=",
    "originContent": "```",
    "translatedContent": "```"
  },
  {
    "row": 44,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 45,
    "rowsha": "rrJjNCNGFYImCsPYoYI0QAF5cy9+tbRmJvLcJLqMRx4=",
    "originContent": "You can override relevant env vars in your `.env.local` ",
    "translatedContent": "你可以像往常一样在你的 `.env.local` 文件中覆盖相关的环境变量，  "
  },
  {
    "row": 46,
    "rowsha": "rL4u3cJ6zuOe5hC4Cw5N53RRqA5lQA5NI2mylcK2HI8=",
    "originContent": "and services in your `config/services.yaml` as usual.",
    "translatedContent": "并在你的 `config/services.yaml` 文件中配置服务。  "
  },
  {
    "row": 47,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 48,
    "rowsha": "kvMNsesvyptreldYQf5xMTHTymid8JPs6qr9A9l1JXo=",
    "originContent": "Then, you can inject `Freddie\\Hub\\HubInterface` in your services so that you can call `$hub->publish($update)`,",
    "translatedContent": "然后，你可以在你的服务中注入 `Freddie\\Hub\\HubInterface`，这样你就可以调用 `$hub->publish($update)`，  "
  },
  {
    "row": 49,
    "rowsha": "MwCz5iKOuQLQHDUokTAj/kltAUUMYWMz28Kc6slDAEk=",
    "originContent": "or listening to dispatched updates in a CLI context 👍",
    "translatedContent": "或者在 CLI 环境中监听分发的更新 👍  "
  },
  {
    "row": 50,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 51,
    "rowsha": "FGxM0to5835qI7jmt1b3GDox3517lICxF/vjV0DwkEI=",
    "originContent": "Keep in mind this only works when using the Redis transport.",
    "translatedContent": "请记住，这仅在使用 Redis 传输时有效。  "
  },
  {
    "row": 52,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 53,
    "rowsha": "lEBSpGbqFdhnTVeDWe5TfmcfPMLrNepwi+uNvc6STFw=",
    "originContent": "⚠️ **Freddie** uses its own routing/authentication system (because of async / event loop). ",
    "translatedContent": "⚠️ **Freddie** 使用它自己的路由/认证系统（因为异步/事件循环）。  "
  },
  {
    "row": 54,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 55,
    "rowsha": "ploDiSPqT39dNJMXcrbw6BoPR/+NGKubOLqEmBJXXfQ=",
    "originContent": "The controllers it exposes cannot be imported in your `routes.yaml`, and get out of your  `security.yaml` scope.",
    "translatedContent": "它暴露的控制器不能在你的 `routes.yaml` 中导入，  "
  },
  {
    "row": 56,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "也不在你的 `security.yaml` 的管理范围内。  "
  },
  {
    "row": 57,
    "rowsha": "Y7/WGgVhslWiyqCi463Qkcp+Mn8voGpAfLsv80G4WNg=",
    "originContent": "## Usage",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 58,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "## 使用方法  "
  },
  {
    "row": 59,
    "rowsha": "rTMjNc+qNIxb1xXDR5hEYiJw1fc4muBwuBsTXVIaIho=",
    "originContent": "```bash",
    "translatedContent": "```bash"
  },
  {
    "row": 60,
    "rowsha": "cc1a6XZoF9JyNh/62VgiOgEXlBnFGBhBJMfMN8c97HQ=",
    "originContent": "./bin/freddie",
    "translatedContent": "./bin/freddie"
  },
  {
    "row": 61,
    "rowsha": "8bkBhHOQsO1+N058HkZOwXtGpCfEh6WtbL0pBkBQg9U=",
    "originContent": "```",
    "translatedContent": "```"
  },
  {
    "row": 62,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 63,
    "rowsha": "YllHknIslJz4cDIFja/QTfRqWAj2lyoudGfnFuX5zzw=",
    "originContent": "It will start a new Mercure hub on `127.0.0.1:8080`. ",
    "translatedContent": "它将在 `127.0.0.1:8080` 启动一个新的 Mercure 集线器。  "
  },
  {
    "row": 64,
    "rowsha": "OVQjkLDbdwbP4TCGg/pwcrZqHc0V9NRmgMcoRmEPZIU=",
    "originContent": "To change this address, use the `X_LISTEN` environment variable:",
    "translatedContent": "要更改此地址，请使用 `X_LISTEN` 环境变量：  "
  },
  {
    "row": 65,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 66,
    "rowsha": "rTMjNc+qNIxb1xXDR5hEYiJw1fc4muBwuBsTXVIaIho=",
    "originContent": "```bash",
    "translatedContent": "```bash"
  },
  {
    "row": 67,
    "rowsha": "ltnJSd5vitkj6VrTpJa/pLrSb9MMfQM4oUuwfx+n/rA=",
    "originContent": "X_LISTEN=\"0.0.0.0:8000\" ./bin/freddie",
    "translatedContent": "X_LISTEN=\"0.0.0.0:8000\" ./bin/freddie"
  },
  {
    "row": 68,
    "rowsha": "8bkBhHOQsO1+N058HkZOwXtGpCfEh6WtbL0pBkBQg9U=",
    "originContent": "```",
    "translatedContent": "```"
  },
  {
    "row": 69,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 70,
    "rowsha": "k0JyAMT+wP0qguawuCzJsTokdj8lZNw8Qlu7r3ztGYg=",
    "originContent": "### Security ",
    "translatedContent": "### 安全性"
  },
  {
    "row": 71,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 72,
    "rowsha": "faubm3e2myoRtjY2AC8Bt1Jiw+RAsBr44Fdik7NSlGc=",
    "originContent": "The default JWT key is `!ChangeMe!` with a `HS256` signature. ",
    "translatedContent": "默认的 JWT 密钥是 `!ChangeMe!`，使用 `HS256` 签名。"
  },
  {
    "row": 73,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 74,
    "rowsha": "Bsx2T1blZ+dDvc5MNiiDexxph8KsoyY8xM/Qn86xR+8=",
    "originContent": "You can set different values by changing the environment variables (in `.env.local` or at the OS level): ",
    "translatedContent": "您可以通过更改环境变量（在 `.env.local` 文件或操作系统级别）来设置不同的值："
  },
  {
    "row": 75,
    "rowsha": "AuJGtJMTt+3CsMSpuRTgdkPNKA4KXkwk/F7h8LuMsXU=",
    "originContent": "`X_LISTEN`, `JWT_SECRET_KEY`, `JWT_ALGORITHM`, `JWT_PUBLIC_KEY` and `JWT_PASSPHRASE` (when using RS512 or ECDSA)",
    "translatedContent": "`X_LISTEN`、`JWT_SECRET_KEY`、`JWT_ALGORITHM`、`JWT_PUBLIC_KEY` 和 `JWT_PASSPHRASE`（使用 RS512 或 ECDSA 时）"
  },
  {
    "row": 76,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 77,
    "rowsha": "R2CQj2sCHQ9jdE64EANcEWcDwt6iZaMOgedCqcqUh4I=",
    "originContent": "Please refer to the [authorization](https://mercure.rocks/spec#authorization) section of the Mercure specification to authenticate as a publisher and/or a subscriber.",
    "translatedContent": "请参考 Mercure 规范的[授权](https://mercure.rocks/spec#authorization)部分，以作为发布者和/或订阅者进行身份验证。"
  },
  {
    "row": 78,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 79,
    "rowsha": "94bi8CEJg2yu6y54LIpe0T8GO9Ozr4DSMTzxvat8I0c=",
    "originContent": "### PHP Transport (default)",
    "translatedContent": "### PHP 传输（默认）"
  },
  {
    "row": 80,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 81,
    "rowsha": "rc/+H4EI54MpfP7K94U0aS3uJJlB2m0O2zrLMTS/iNw=",
    "originContent": "By default, the hub will run as a simple event-dispatcher, in a single PHP process.",
    "translatedContent": "默认情况下，集线器将作为一个简单的事件分发器运行，在单个 PHP 进程中。"
  },
  {
    "row": 82,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 83,
    "rowsha": "6YnG1awABTP1av4j1MJrLcy9sFJBVO/O8msO1Jkl82I=",
    "originContent": "It can fit common needs for a basic usage, but using this transport prevents scalability,",
    "translatedContent": "它适合基本使用的常见需求，但使用此传输会阻止可扩展性，"
  },
  {
    "row": 84,
    "rowsha": "GggEnW4kNDaTPsDsFoL4RYtCUc8oOo2Zh0u5zduZOBU=",
    "originContent": "as opening another process won't share the same event emitter.",
    "translatedContent": "因为开启另一个进程不会共享相同的事件发射器。"
  },
  {
    "row": 85,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 86,
    "rowsha": "AD25LLWwozRdVgUsiLGPHXRpB20fKjK0V/juSAmEd18=",
    "originContent": "It's still prefectly usable as soon as :",
    "translatedContent": "只要满足以下条件，它仍然完全可用："
  },
  {
    "row": 87,
    "rowsha": "x4wpYGxkGKFLNs6ah63201qQbzvnmMCh6+OZQcfUr9M=",
    "originContent": "- You don't expect more than a few hundreds updates per second",
    "translatedContent": "- 您不期望每秒超过几百次更新"
  },
  {
    "row": 88,
    "rowsha": "Q9SkX2XJa3In86vel6MmrY5GOm1XxofN1EgCDahKvsY=",
    "originContent": "- Your application is served from a single server.",
    "translatedContent": "- 您的应用程序由单台服务器提供服务。"
  },
  {
    "row": 89,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 90,
    "rowsha": "NWGAQrzN67e6aXUxkpktD9pBUtTg0aSDvehkofwli74=",
    "originContent": "### Redis transport",
    "translatedContent": "### Redis 传输"
  },
  {
    "row": 91,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 92,
    "rowsha": "M5dn3H2niY9nOtuaZC4TtxvKgUxJC6YRThFJbyghxRU=",
    "originContent": "On the other hand, you can launch the hub on **multiple ports** and/or **multiple servers** with a Redis transport",
    "translatedContent": "另一方面，您可以在**多个端口**和/或**多台服务器**上使用 Redis 传输启动集线器"
  },
  {
    "row": 93,
    "rowsha": "cDsMfIaz0x0uYUI3b51g19oqNz3l6AlF5Iq84Oi56i0=",
    "originContent": "(as soon as they share the same Redis instance), and optionally use a load-balancer to distribute the traffic.",
    "translatedContent": "（只要它们共享相同的 Redis 实例），并且可选地使用负载均衡器来分配流量。"
  },
  {
    "row": 94,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 95,
    "rowsha": "x/5asic0ZKhvHitsQ1ABVnzrMNcJnL3P2RuxyH9xjOY=",
    "originContent": "The [official open-source version](https://mercure.rocks/docs/hub/install) of the hub doesn't allow scaling ",
    "translatedContent": "集线器的[官方开源版本](https://mercure.rocks/docs/hub/install)不允许扩展，"
  },
  {
    "row": 96,
    "rowsha": "VdJ++Yogbn1+GjpL+1npjJO49CPYQMqfxa1iHkROaPs=",
    "originContent": "because of concurrency restrictions on the _bolt_ transport.",
    "translatedContent": "因为 _bolt_ 传输存在并发限制。"
  },
  {
    "row": 97,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 98,
    "rowsha": "DFWpwWCDDHZBLCabFWo89ORCId/YzEl8ggUZ/+RltJ8=",
    "originContent": "To launch the hub with the Redis transport, change the `TRANSPORT_DSN` environment variable:",
    "translatedContent": "要使用 Redis 传输启动集线器，请更改 `TRANSPORT_DSN` 环境变量："
  },
  {
    "row": 99,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 100,
    "rowsha": "rTMjNc+qNIxb1xXDR5hEYiJw1fc4muBwuBsTXVIaIho=",
    "originContent": "```bash",
    "translatedContent": "```bash"
  },
  {
    "row": 101,
    "rowsha": "YIgnZ8QLr8CJeAbnqetcNQwnQpltnn+nBnV3/GxncBA=",
    "originContent": "TRANSPORT_DSN=\"redis://127.0.0.1:6379\" ./bin/freddie",
    "translatedContent": "TRANSPORT_DSN=\"redis://127.0.0.1:6379\" ./bin/freddie"
  },
  {
    "row": 102,
    "rowsha": "8bkBhHOQsO1+N058HkZOwXtGpCfEh6WtbL0pBkBQg9U=",
    "originContent": "```",
    "translatedContent": "```"
  },
  {
    "row": 103,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 104,
    "rowsha": "80r3GYDl95JAHTUB4U2LPo838ojMru55IQiawyrsW54=",
    "originContent": "Optional parameters you can pass in the DSN's query string:",
    "translatedContent": "可选参数可以通过 DSN 的查询字符串传递："
  },
  {
    "row": 105,
    "rowsha": "LX6iEVuNTEO3VyBh3Ss4hMdLqlWAhPWuoKfadMRDQsg=",
    "originContent": "- `pingInterval` - regularly ping Redis connection, which will help detect outages (default `2.0`)",
    "translatedContent": "- `pingInterval` - 定期 ping Redis 连接，有助于检测故障（默认 `2.0`）"
  },
  {
    "row": 106,
    "rowsha": "48yB7/rb0CVYsbaoC3sUz+GVgieZzC3KPdrnOD8Qr7Q=",
    "originContent": "- `readTimeout` - max duration in seconds of a ping or publish request (default `0.0`: considered disabled)",
    "translatedContent": "- `readTimeout` - ping 或发布请求的最大持续时间（秒）（默认 `0.0`：视为禁用）"
  },
  {
    "row": 107,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 108,
    "rowsha": "n13N+MXdXudJ6oKnctNoanUbNqvJayXAf6SkYPL86iQ=",
    "originContent": "_Alternatively, you can set this variable into `.env.local`._",
    "translatedContent": "_或者，您也可以将此变量设置到 `.env.local`。_"
  },
  {
    "row": 109,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
